            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="har.00039.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey</name>
                    <date when="1889-03-24">March 24 '89</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Thanks for the money &#38; order wh' were duly rec'd&#8212;I have sent the book<ptr target="n4195"/> to
                you by express, &#38; when you get it safely please send me a card notifying me. Am
                laid up here disabled &#38; paralyzed, but getting along, &#38; comfortable
                enough.</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Best love to you &#38; yours<ptr target="har.00039_n1"/>&#8212;</salute>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
                <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="har.00039.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
            </closer>
        </body>
